意思，阻你小小位，希望靠呢隻歌可以凝聚到更多人。"},{"pid":"dde5607e480e6220f9c535f70ddd3f8d8b963c0d","tid":1451012,"uid":304180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:06.000Z","msg":"大大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27937f72e904a81641f153c653a01f42f463f1cf","tid":1451012,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:13.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家 準備長期作戰<br />\n聽日唔好再玩接機 笑笑口和理非<br />\n記住個女仔半邊面係血既樣<br />\n記住班黑警1m距離內開槍+掉人落電梯<br />\n記住依家有幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日12/8 Full gear塞爆+癱瘓 成個機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔唱歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔接機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔衝禁區<br />\n<br />\n保持憤怒 統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e6e4a5522998bae80f84fec4eaa49ef5d17cb8","tid":1451012,"uid":282783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:19.000Z","msg":"612，721，811"},{"pid":"ea183c530ae0dc882d673165974db507f665d94e","tid":1451012,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f4807ed62cf723e7f972691a15c022a6a96fe42","tid":1451012,"uid":84657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証"},{"pid":"ee6661a2477edfd7afbc3e7a3f9c45bb976eef2f","tid":1451012,"uid":148390,"like":1,"dis