y":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:37:04.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5217f311670ed26b7e6938cc8ceb7f55a48e6cd5","tid":1451012,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:42:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"658a4cf4c5e6b30ee8535e6701ead516d954d218","tid":1451012,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:47:57.000Z","msg":"直接去 Facebook page 啦<br />\n<br />\n民陣 facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=5e34d9db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n<br />\n推到有818香港人大遊行！"},{"pid":"8e3f7d2d46e6f8072e94b717d28f39b53136e65e","tid":1451012,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:05:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"53189322f1c1d7a2c4e18c033d830a7b1bdcac0c","tid":1451012,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:18:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"30d5f38e3451dd8ea7b44ee403e1f7dd4541030c","tid":1451012,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:53:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a3195c0de370f25bcf05128de9acaf92d380bfc","tid":1451012,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對港鐵不合作運動全民跳閘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n<br />\n2.和理非要癱瘓機場<br />\n記住係針對貨運嚟搞!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宣佈成立國民自衛隊對抗警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷被捕兄弟討回公道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線太多手足比捉 一定要升級癱瘓機場 全民打狗 選擇一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1b025f806cc7c813afa5866876cefc5c0692211","tid":1451012,"uid":276894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69570ebf10bb642c1336c71b8cb3b9e484a9504","tid":1451012,"uid":44445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"經過今晚，我知道大家一定會畀香港警察嘅所作所為搞到好嬲<br />\n我知道你哋一定會覺得自己好似咩都做唔到咁<br />\n但我正正想講嘅係，我哋如果真係咁，就中哂政府嘅計！<br />\n佢用香港警察搞咁多嘢<br />\n第一，係想滅聲，等人唔敢再出嚟<br />\n第二，利用我哋依家對香港警察嘅仇恨，令成件事個矛頭轉哂去香港警察度，之後就可以理直氣壯話我哋活動變哂質<br />\n所以，我哋一定要再企出嚟，話畀政府聽，我哋唔會中計！<br />\n今晚香港警察嘅行為，我相信全香港嘅市民都會有眼見到<br />\n所以我希望民陣可以利用今晚嘅事號召全香港真正愛香港嘅人再出嚟，<br />\n話畀政府知，就算你哋背後做幾多手腳，民意都係唔會改變！！<br />\n2014年放咗咁&ldquo;少&rdquo;催淚彈（同2019年比）都激發到咁多香港人走出嚟<br />\n我相信2019年嘅今日都唔會例外<br />\n<br />\n但今次遊行完切記真係要散！<br />\n因為我知道有好多人（特別係一班年紀大嘅中產）最近唔出嚟都係因為驚每次完都會有衝突。<br />\n點解我哋要和理非咁遊呢次行，因為呢班人都係我哋嘅同路人。<br />\n佢哋就係一班人入面走得比較慢嘅一群，但我哋都唔可以唔理佢哋就咁衝。<br />\n我哋要贏就要一齊贏！<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以好似警察咁畀仇恨蒙蔽自己<br />\n雖然呢句好左膠feel，但我覺得大家要切記<br />\n香港人，加油！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:55:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad902c03dda481335e728831a97f4bfbc6f4520","tid":1451012,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:56:33.000Z","msg":"入紙未"},{"pid":"f7a8af7af92b0c85a681e0fe2a2ce484650dcc55","tid":1451012,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:57:43.000Z","msg":"重點係行完入機場"},{"pid":"876f7b397c92e77cbda8c727cf5313daafac533d","tid":1451012,"uid":239143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:58:01.000Z","msg":"屌、冇人推 ？"},{"pid":"dba5d495febe42b68bbba26186a7bf8b89649c82","tid":1451012,"uid":61991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi